
	
1.按钮
	btn btn-default
	btn btn-primary
	btn btn-success
	btn btn-info
	btn btn-warning
	btn btn-danger
	btn btn-link
	btn-lg
	btn-sm
	btn-xs
	btn-block
	disabled 禁用按钮，非样式，直接属性
		可以做按钮的标签，button ,input type="button",a,submit
2.图片
bg-primary	bg-success	bg-info	bg-warning	bg-danger	img-circle
	img-thumbnail
3.辅助类
	文本颜色
		text-muted	text-primary text-success text-info	text-warning	text-danger
	背景颜色
		bg-primary	bg-success	bg-info	bg-warning	bg-danger
	关闭
		close
	更多
		caret <span class="caret"></span>
	浮动
		pull-right pull-left
	清除浮动
		clearfix <div class="clearfix"></div>
	居中
		center-block
	显示和隐藏
		hide show
4.响应式工具
	img-responsive
	table-responsive

组件：
1.glyhpicons图标
	字体图标：glyphicon glyphicon-triangle-right
2.下拉菜单
	dropdown
	<div class="dropdown">
		<button class="btn btn-primary" data-toggle="dropdown">更多课程<span class="caret"></span></button>
		<ul class="dropdown">
			<li>百度</li>
			<li>谷歌</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	分隔线
		divider
	标题
		dropdown-header
3.按钮组
	btn-group
	<div class="btn-group">
		<button class="btn btn-primary">百度</button>
		<button class="btn btn-danger">谷歌</button>
		<button class="btn btn-info">搜索</button>
4.按钮工具箱
	.btn-toolbar 里面放btn-group
	按钮尺寸
		btn-group 里加的
		btn-group-lg btn-group-sm 	btn-group-sx
5.嵌入式按钮组
	<div class="btn-group">
		<button class="btn btn-primary">百度</button>
		<button class="btn btn-default">谷歌</button>
		<div class="btn-group btn-toggle">
			<button class="btn btn-primary">更多<span class="caret"></span><button>
			<ul class="dropdown-menu">
				<li><a href="#">百度</a></li>
				<li><a href="#">谷歌</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
	竖向排列
	.btn-toggle
	.btn-group-vertical
6.表单：
	.from-group
	.form-control
	.checkbox
	.radio
	内联表单：.form-inline
	内部嵌套：input-group ,input-group-addon
	水平排列：form-horizontal ,
	静态字体：form-control-static .
	表单元素禁用和只读 disabled readonly 
	区域禁用：fieldset class="disabled"
	表单验证：表单框颜色 has-success,has-warning,has-error
	输入框内字符图标：div上加has-feedback ,后面input 内部加 span class="... form-control-feedback"
	表单框尺寸：input-lg,input-sm
	表单框帮助提示：<p class="help-block">
7.输入框组
	input-group
	input-group-addon
	input-group-lg,input-group-sm

	输入文字，checkbox，radio
	<div class="input-group-addon">
		<input type="checkbox">
		<input type="redio">
	输入btn
	<div class="input-group-btn">
		<button class="btn btn-primary">
	输入dropdownlist
	<div class="input-group-btn">
		<input type="text" class="form-control"/>
		<div class="input-group-btn">
			<button class="btn btn-default" data-toggle="dropdown">XmFx<span class="caret"><span></button>
			<ul class="dropdown-menu">
				<li><a>Panda</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
8.导航
	分两种，标签页式导航，胶囊式导航
	标签页
	<ul class="nav nav-tabs">
		<li class="active"><a>项目管理</a></li>
		<li><a>金融管理</a></li>
	</ul>
	胶囊式导航
	<ul class="nav nav-pills nav-stacked">
	</ul>

